---

<PlaybookLayout
  title="Writing Copy When You Hate Writing Copy"
  metaTitle="Copywriting for Developers Who Hate Writing | CodeToCash"
  metaDescription="Frameworks, templates, and a systematic approach to writing sales copy for developers. No creativity required — just fill in the blanks."
