        <p class="font-mono text-sm text-coral mb-2">"From [before state] to [after state] — [customer name]'s story"</p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Example: <span class="text-gray-200">"From 0 to $8K MRR in 4 months — how Marcus built his first SaaS"</span></p>
