        <p class="font-mono text-sm text-coral mb-2">"Finally, a [product type] that [specific thing your customers keep asking for]"</p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Example: <span class="text-gray-200">"Finally, an email tool that doesn't require a marketing degree to use"</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Objection-Busting Headlines -->
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-4">Objection-Busting Headlines</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Preemptively address skepticism. Best for audiences who have been burned before.</p>

    <div class="space-y-3 mb-6">
      <div class="p-4 bg-[#0d0d20] border border-white/10 rounded-xl">
        <p class="font-mono text-sm text-coral mb-2">"[Desired outcome] — no [objection] required"</p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Example: <span class="text-gray-200">"Launch your first ad campaign — no marketing experience required"</span></p>
