      <div class="p-4 bg-[#0d0d20] border border-white/10 rounded-xl">
        <p class="font-mono text-sm text-coral mb-2">"You don't need [what they think they need] to [outcome]"</p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Example: <span class="text-gray-200">"You don't need a big following to get your first 100 customers"</span></p>
