      <div class="p-4 bg-[#0d0d20] border border-white/10 rounded-xl">
        <p class="font-mono text-sm text-coral mb-2">"[Product] for people who [don't think they belong in this category]"</p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Example: <span class="text-gray-200">"Email marketing for developers who swore they'd never do email marketing"</span></p>
